[[iHeartRadio|iHeartRadio]]（2020年）}}'''iHeartRadio音樂獎'''（{{Lang-en|'''iHeartRadio Music Awards'''}}）是由[[網路電台|網路電台]][[iHeartRadio|iHeartRadio]]於2014年創立[[音樂|音樂]]頒獎典禮，旨在表彰過去一年中最受歡迎的藝術家和音樂。優勝者根據累積的投票數據選出，公眾可在數個類別中投票。<ref>{{Cite web|title=iHeartRadio Music Awards: 5 things you need to know|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/music/2014/05/02/iheartradio-music-awards-5-things-you-need-to-know/8577809/|accessdate=2020-11-14|last=Ryan|first=Patrick|work=USA TODAY|language=en-US|archive-date=2015-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150317233752/http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/music/2014/05/02/iheartradio-music-awards-5-things-you-need-to-know/8577809/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

首屆典禮於2014年5月1日在[[美國|美國]][[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]][[雪蘭劇院|雪蘭劇院]]（Shrine Auditorium）舉行。前兩屆由[[全國廣播公司|全國廣播公司]]現場直播；2016年到2018年，換由[[透納廣播公司|透納廣播公司]]電視頻道、[[特纳电视网|特納電視網]]和[[TruTV|TruTV]]負責轉播。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Turner Cable Networks to Air 2016 iHeartRadio Music Awards|url=https://variety.com/2015/tv/ratings/turner-cable-networks-to-air-2016-iheartradio-music-awards-1201514555/|accessdate=2020-11-14|date=2015-06-08|last=Kissell|first=Rick|work=Variety|language=en-US|archive-date=2018-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180617142249/https://variety.com/2015/tv/ratings/turner-cable-networks-to-air-2016-iheartradio-music-awards-1201514555/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=TBS - Turner Broadcasting Systems Inc. (via Public) / iHeartRadio Music Awards to air this Sunday, March 5, live on Turner's TBS, TNT and truTV|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180617142239/http://www.publicnow.com/view/D37BD361A36B63AEC1960586B83DBEB6A9404D5A?2017-03-02-15:30:45+00:00-xxx2353|accessdate=2020-11-14|date=2018-06-17|work=web.archive.org}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Drake Leads iHeartRadio Music Awards Nominations {{!}} Access Online|url=https://accessonlinefrontprod.ao.apps.nbcuni.com/articles/drake-leads-iheartradio-music-awards-nominations|accessdate=2020-11-14|work=Access|language=en}}</ref>[[2019年iHeartRadio音樂獎|第六屆年度iHeartRadio音樂獎]]於2019年3月14日在洛杉磯的[[微軟劇院|微軟劇院]]舉行，是首屆由[[福斯廣播公司|福斯]]轉播。獎盃由紐約Society Awards公司製造。

由於[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|嚴重特殊傳染性肺炎]]持續延燒，2020年的頒獎典禮被取消。獲獎名單於9月4日至7日揭曉。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Here are the latest major events that have been canceled or postponed because of the coronavirus outbreak, including the 2020 Tokyo Olympics, Burning Man, and the 74th Annual Tony Awards|url=https://www.businessinsider.com/major-events-cancelled-or-postponed-due-to-the-coronavirus-2020|accessdate=2020-11-14|last=Casado|first=Joey Hadden, Laura|work=Business Insider|archive-date=2020-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200305170915/https://www.businessinsider.com/major-events-cancelled-or-postponed-due-to-the-coronavirus-2020|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 概述 ==
提名基於[[iHeartRadio|iHeartRadio]]排行榜的結果。根據聽眾的反饋、表現等播放情況與數據；來自iHeartRadio平台的數位串流媒體數據，包括銷售、社交、在線影片數據以及BigChampagne和[[Shazam_(服務)|Shazam]]的標籤。每週兩小時的節目《iHeartRadio倒數》會突出顯示iHeartRadio排行榜中前20名[[當代流行電台|當代流行]]歌曲。<ref>{{Cite web|title=NBC to Televise Clear Channels First Ever iHeartRadio Music Awards Live May 1|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160404173149/http://www.iheartmedia.com/Pages/NBC-to-Televise-Clear-Channels-First-Ever-iHeartRadio-Music-Awards-Live-May-1.aspx|accessdate=2020-11-14|date=2016-04-04|work=web.archive.org}}</ref>此外，每個公共投票類別都將social[[主題標籤|主題標籤]]作為主要投票機制。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Frequently Asked Questions {{!}} iHeartRadio|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305025000/http://news.iheart.com/articles/iheartradio-music-awards-490103/frequently-asked-questions-13264323/|accessdate=2020-11-14|date=2016-03-05|work=web.archive.org}}</ref>

